Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:23.46,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}憧れを書きとめて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:26.21,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}いつか叶える日のために
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:31.68,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折り目つけたあのページを　開きたい時がきた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:37.02,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}巻き起こるアレコレで　見失うこともあるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:39.77,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ねっ、大丈夫　踏み出してる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:42.40,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}はじまりは想定外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:45.19,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君が消せないまま残した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:47.94,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}寂しがりだった記憶さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:52.03,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}読み替えてみせるよ　明るい方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:57.45,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}たったそれだけで全てが変わる気がするから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:58.75,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.79,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}だから　さあおいで　そのままで！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:04.63,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}弱虫も隠さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:05.84,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:09.51,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夢乗せ　待ち合わせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:15.39,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}この冒険記を綴る中　君の名を呼んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:21.89,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}もう迷子じゃない　一緒の旅を始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:29.23,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そう…きみと、わたし、もっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:23.46,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}記下你的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:26.21,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}以迎接它變成現實的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:31.68,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折疊起來的書頁  正在呼喚著我去翻閱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:37.02,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}揚起的風沙塵土  可能會讓你迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:39.77,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但是不要擔心  我們在堅定前行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:42.40,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}只是開端有點意想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:45.19,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}你記錄下的寂寞經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:47.94,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}無法擦去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:52.03,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但我會解讀成未來的財富
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:57.45,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}如此小的努力就能讓我感到世界煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:58.75,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.79,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}所以  跟我來吧  就這樣出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:04.63,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}沒有什麼好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:05.84,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:09.51,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}放飛夢想  相約明天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:15.39,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}書寫這篇歷險記的時候  即使呼喚你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:21.89,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}那也不意味著迷路  而是共同啟程的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:29.23,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}沒錯…你與我 不會停步！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:53.69,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}始まりのベル　鍵をかける音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:22:01.49,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}流れゆく間に大人になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:07.23,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}走り　はしゃぎ　過ごす日々が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.47,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠ざかるときがくる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:15.97,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ここで出した答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:28.16,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ああ　どこかで語り継げたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:33.44,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}迷いながら歩く人波を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:37.77,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}照らし出す光になれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:45.98,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}包まれてたグリーンベルトの先
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:54.32,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}続く明日を目指してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:53.69,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}起始之鈴  上鎖之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:22:01.49,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在它們的流淌中  我們逐漸成長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:07.23,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}奔跑歡笑的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.47,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}終歸會遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:15.97,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}此刻得出的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:28.16,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只要將它流傳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:33.44,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}即使是迷惘而行的人潮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:37.77,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}也能將其引領
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:45.98,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}沿著綠蔭大道走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:54.32,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}就能到達期望的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第10本了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧京太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來能見到他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從我第一次見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意就不曾改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論你是什麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都想接受你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我懂得了重要的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想正視自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你在  我就別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們永不分離
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長  你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  我只是按佳奈助你的劇本演啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一幕還是重寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際一演讓我明白了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.63,0:01:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你會這麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.34,0:01:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直對寫劇本很有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過筧學長的精確指導已經耗光我血槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次寫劇本能有這種水平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.66,0:01:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,題材也很適合海邊的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的稱讚好微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式上演時沒人買帳怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是委託
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是活躍氣氛的短劇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得有趣滑稽就行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畏首畏尾可不是你的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:02:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的風格呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候一定讓全場爆笑不已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.50,TXTJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\fs14\pos(320,76)}汐美學園同好會主辦  最早的開海祭!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.50,TXTJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\fs14\pos(320,131)}古式游泳法全式實操
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種游法叫羽交伸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會對男人的兜襠布感興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  去看接下來的短劇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（圖書部  短劇 「赤裸的女王」）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想承認自己是傻瓜的愚蠢巨乳女王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被騙子騙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然根本沒有漂亮的禮服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但面對豐滿的胸部  沒人會說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是階級社會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子  請看身穿艷麗禮服的二位麗人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮服？不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只看到女王和公主身穿內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實不相瞞  這禮服是特製的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道王子看不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所認可的下任國王怎麼會是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親所言極是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:05:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我未來的夫君不可能是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  王子  別娶公主娶我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親莫要說笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子請對我一心一意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本看不到什麼禮服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我是個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在我感覺這也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光著身子耍威風的女王  真是傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人能反抗女王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我可以大賺一筆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  王子也穿上這美妙的服裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我憧憬的王子也對笨蛋女王唯命是從
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來救他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王沒穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子  不要被區區脂肪球蒙蔽雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這下流王子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是心有期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得戲劇會成功  大家都會說有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭報應了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種配角還想出風頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒臉見櫻庭學姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但寫劇本很快樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快樂的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我消沉個什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴木我專注搞笑三十年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓人笑正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太勉強自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞的佳奈好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天學長挺帥氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  高峰學長烤的肉很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:08:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉的男人真是萌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈你喜歡筧學長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你冷不丁地說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想瞞著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒資格讓別人喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是圖書部接受了這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒想到能和千莉你變得這麼要好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想需要理由和資格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千莉  剛才的話再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於是心意相通了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們跨越那粉色的屏障吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐美祭？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們學校的學園祭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年都非常熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們今年很想上汐美祭的主舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓學生會認可我們的成績
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才舉辦了開海祭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但學生會說還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這種同好會想上主舞台是不對的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:32.88,TXTJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H635d64&\frz-15\pos(320.2,198.8)}學生會室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再向學生會請求一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是副會長多岐川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她負責汐美祭的事務手續
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓她列席了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於增加汐美祭的展示場地一事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結論是  由於空間所限  不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就沒餘地談了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是來交涉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會做事一直考慮全校學生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因增加場地而導致警備不足引起事故的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書部會負責嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多岐川  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會再考慮此事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵  像剛才那樣的態度不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠正確的言論  是得不到支持的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應對圖書部我一個人就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副會長的意見倒是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是等學生會行動  還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有我們幫得上忙的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  乾等不符合我們的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  盡力而為吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事不宜遲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有主意就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要提高同好會的認知度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  能在校內搞活動就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活動成功的話  學生會也會認可的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會那麼順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果失敗的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  佳奈助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我血液中喜歡熱鬧的因子沸騰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來進行個圖書部劇本的活動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儀左大人也贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是對貓過敏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癢  癢  好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢  好想撓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下疤痕的話  可愛的胳膊就糟蹋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多了  白崎學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的只有這些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫上你的忙  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴木真是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胳膊沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我獲得了白崎學姐的治癒能量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請勿擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在勉強自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦  筧學長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別騙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時的佳奈助會藏得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在介意之前的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長你才是  到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前都是視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的風格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果成為牧羊人  讀佳奈助的書的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就算如此你也想當牧羊人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不惜放棄與白崎她們的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的戀愛運
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝作偶然  去找意中人商量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許就能恩恩愛愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
