Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:31.46,TXTG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBDA5ED&\an1\fs14\frz344.2\pos(118.4,292.4)\blur1}幸運物品{\r}\N{\c&HA39CA9&\fs14\frz344.2\blur1}圖書館的書
